SUMMARY:Firelane 1 to Dogwood (Trail Run in Forest Park)
DESCRIPTION:Northwest Trail Runners\n**Distance**: 6 mile trail run\n**Gain**: 474 feet\n**Start**: Top of Firelane 1\n**After**: Von Ebert In Cedar Mill\n**Parking**: Please carpool\, parking is limited.\n**Bring**: HEADLAMPS!\n\nThis trail run starts with a fun downhill section from the top of Firelane 1 to get us warmed up and then we wind along Wildwood to 53rd. We’ll lollipop on Dogwood then run back on Wildwood to Firelane 1.\n\nThe route:\n• Start down Firelane 1 \\| \\.25 miles\n• Right on Wildwood \\| 2 miles\n• Right on Keil Trail \\|\\.2 miles\n• Left down Dogwood \\| \\.7 miles\n• Left on Wildwood \\| 2\\.6 miles\n• Left up Firelane 1 \\| \\.25 miles\n\nLink to route: https://www.strava.com/routes/2814275248326498014\n\nAfter the run\, we'll enjoy Pizza and Beer:\nVon Ebert Pizzeria & Taproom\n11800 NW Cedar Falls Dr #110\nPortland\, OR 97229\n\nSee you on the trails\,\nHosted by: Arne\nNorthwest Trail Runners
